  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -0.230624131518415         -6.2756          -144.72          -605.50
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.047624096174791          1.2959            29.88           125.04
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.030326744732296         -0.8252           -19.03           -79.62
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
  Total Pauli Repulsion:                 0.267194272061347          7.2707           167.67           701.52
 (Total Pauli Repulsion =
  Delta E^Pauli in BB paper)

